node.text:
Entries for this October’s Summer Shredding Classic are coming in and filling up fast. If you want to step on stage in any of the following divisions, click the link in my bio or go to www.summershreddingevents.com to reserve your slot.

1️⃣Men’s Physique
2️⃣Women’s Bikini
3️⃣Men’s Classic Physique
4️⃣Women’s Figure
5️⃣Men’s Bodybuilding
6️⃣Transformation Class (for both men and women)

#summershredding

node.text: There will never be a “perfect time” to start. That moment simply doesn’t exist. It’s simple. Find something you’re passionate about. Set a goal that intimidates you. A goal that seems far fetched and a little crazy at first... Then... Execute. Find a way. If you don’t find one, make one. Don’t stop until you’re there. #summershredding2020

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Christian Guzman on July 29, 2021 tagging @nabilelh_, @muralmule, @alphalete, @officialalphaletegym, and @official_alphaland. May be an image of 1 person, indoor and brick wall.

node.text:
You’ll never work a day in your life if you take the time to truly find out what you love doing. The thing that at times - can scare the living shit out of you… But also bring you to tears of accomplishment.

The thing you can look at when you’re done and say, “Damn… I actually f****ng did what I said I was going to do. I refused to take any easy way out. I did this RIGHT - even though it sounded crazy at first”.

When you first get this special feeling/moment - you get absolutely hooked. Hungry to taste that level of self-accomplishment/success again.

I promise you guys what’s in store for the remainder of this Summer Shredding season is something like you (or I) have never seen before.

Be sure to follow the most challenging & intense chapter of our decade-long YouTube journey. 

Oh - and turn on your notifications 🚨💪🏽

Link in bio 🐺

@nabilelh_

Bet on yourself. You’ll never lose if you bet on yourself.
